<br>
There are about a million different ways to do this. Play to your strength.<br>
<br>
If you are a great recruiter, get your own MB wizzies or a guild that can form 36 60's in twenty minutes.<br>
<br>
If you are a great negotiator, work out a compromise with the MB wizards.<br>
<br>
If you are a great player, make your mid-tier guild a high level guild.<br>
<br>
If you are a great thinker, come up with an alliance that will watch Sev for you and figure out ways to help out that alliance.<br>
<br>
If you are a great trader, then buy a wizzie VS or Phin MQ and trade it for a green scale. <br>
<br>
There are a million ways to skin a cat. I am sure that between all the members of your guild, you can come up with something.<br>
<br>
