I call BS.  It has nothing to do with Wizards feeling 'left out'.  It has to do with the ability to do something with a high reward and minimal risk.  If Rogues could do it, they would.  If Warriors could, they would.  On and on.  There will always be players willing to garner high returns with low risk regardless of class or difficulty in leveling up.  Lack of groups doesn't have a damn thing to do with it, so stop throwing that around.  Its a red herring.<br>
